---
title: Chicken and Butter Bean Cassoulet with Green Beans, Pesto and Rocket
description: Inspired by a French classic, this Chicken & Butter Bean Cassoulet with Green Beans, Pesto and Rocket is rich, delicious and flavourful. Serve alongside fresh salad and a crusty baguette on warm summer evenings with friends and family, and let everyone dig in.
